::Feline::

She moved her head back, her face barely missing the blade, but her 
already hurt shoulder caught the blade as she tried to dodge. It 
slided down to the metal center of her shoulder.  She roared out and 
slashed at Blenders face with bother her front claws and tried to 
bite his neck or shoulder. She was extremely angery and wasn't going 
to hold back.
